    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Forming process in which heated plastic sheet is drawn against the mold surface by evacuating the air between it and the mold.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000038881/Stein, Construction Glossary (1980)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Proceso de formado en el cual una lámina caliente de plástico es adherida contra la superficie del molde evacuando el aire entre ésta y el molde.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Vormingsproces waarbij verhitte, plastic bladen tegen de wanden van de vorm worden getrokken door de ruimte tussen het plastic en de vorm luchtledig te maken.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
